name: Coraline Jones
description:
"UTOPIA" is a cartoon project (until then never finished) that made me find the concept and aesthetics of my art.
 is this the 15/? "UTOPIC PROFILE" season drawings - 
the eyes are always the same, the light seems to come from a single universal point and the character is always in utopia, living in utopia... Coraline Jones (halloween edition)
